<Layout title="Why Lily House Is the Leading Montessori School in Durbanville — Lily House" description="A look inside our farm-based Montessori campus in Durbanville.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/blog">← Back to Blog</a></p>
      <h1>Why Lily House Is the Leading Montessori School in Durbanville</h1>
      <p class="subtitle" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">April 13, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?w=1200&q=80" alt="Lily House Durbanville campus" style="width:100%;border-radius:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;" />

      <p>Set against the rolling vineyards and orchards of the Durbanville valley, Lily House Durbanville offers a truly unique educational experience. Our farm-based campus provides children with space to explore, grow, and learn in an environment that celebrates both nature and academic rigour.</p>

      <h2>Education That Blossoms in Nature</h2>

      <p>Under the leadership of Tasneem Khan, our Durbanville campus embodies the Montessori philosophy in a setting that few schools can match. Here's what makes our Durbanville campus the leading choice for families:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Farm-based learning environment</strong> — children connect with nature daily, fostering environmental stewardship</li>
        <li><strong>Mixed-age classrooms</strong> — peer learning that builds leadership and collaboration skills</li>
        <li><strong>Montessori-certified guides</strong> — dedicated educators who nurture each child's innate curiosity</li>
        <li><strong>Comprehensive programmes</strong> — from toddler through preschool and primary years</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Our daily routines include outdoor exploration, practical life skills, and hands-on learning with authentic Montessori materials. We prepare children not just for their next educational step, but for life.</p>

      <p>Come see why Lily House Durbanville is the leading Montessori school in the area. Book a tour and experience our philosophy in action.</p>

      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:3rem;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent">Book a Tour</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

